"                    the <strong>Sales\n"
"                        App</strong> to quickly shoot over tailored quotations for B2B leads or\n"
"                    custom customer requests, or use the <strong>Subscription App</strong> for new\n"
"                    members."
msgstr ""

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Full Restaurant Capabilities:</strong> Do you have a kitchen or\n"
"                            seated dining area? Map out a visual table layout right in the system\n"
"                            and integrate a digital <strong>Kitchen Display System (KDS)</strong> to\n"
"                            seamlessly coordinate orders between the floor and the kitchen."
