msgstr ""

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Purpose:</strong> Designed for social play, allowing individual players\n"
"                    to sign up and join open, existing games."
msgstr ""

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Shareable Court Resources:</strong> Because the courts are configured as <strong>shareable\n"
"                    resources</strong>, multiple players can register for the same court\n"
"                    simultaneously. The system will continue to accept registrations for a slot as\n"
"                    long as there are open spots available on that court."
msgstr ""

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
