"<strong>Smart Pricelists:</strong> Link these membership levels to custom\n"
"                    pricelists. The system will automatically apply preferential rates, bar\n"
"                    discounts, or free bookings whenever the member makes a purchase."
msgstr ""

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Smart Upselling:</strong> The system automatically maximizes revenue. For\n"
"                    example, when a customer purchases a racket, the eShop strategically suggests\n"
"                    relevant add-ons like towels or balls before checkout."
msgstr ""

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
