"<strong>Streamlined Workflows:</strong> Easily organize your menu into clear\n"
"                    product categories to create an intuitive, fast-paced checkout screen for your\n"
"                    bar staff."
msgstr ""

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Subscription-Driven Tiers:</strong> Define your membership packages as\n"
"                    products in the <strong>Subscription App</strong>. When a customer buys one,\n"
"                    Odoo automatically assigns a specific partner level directly to their customer\n"
"                    profile."
msgstr ""

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Unified Management:</strong> Oversee bar-specific inventory, track\n"
"                    customer tabs, and seamlessly accept every payment method your venue offers from\n"
"                    one screen."
msgstr ""

